  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess the efficacy of periodontal treatment in diabetic patient. Patients
      will be randomized in the periodontal group or in the control group. The control group will
      received a periodontal treatment after the study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
