  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patient suffering from a periodontitis

          -  patient with : 7,0% &lt; Hemoglobin A1c &lt; 9,5%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  If an hospitalization is planned within the next 4 months

          -  Patient suffering from chronic infectious pathology (HIV, hepatitis C virus, hepatitis
             B virus, mononucleosis)

          -  Renal insufficiency

          -  Contra indication for amoxicilline or clindamycin

          -  Antithrombotic treatment

          -  Liver disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
